title: Death From Above 1979 The Biggest Collection
description:
This the new release, more music!
But i want to warn you boys and girls!!
There wouldn't not be band in the world like DFA 1979 so go to store or to amazon or elsewhere and buy their cds! they are great!be sure, i have a lot, BUT if you have heads up on clear vinyl or double pink vinyl yaw,iam please e-mail me at (meetnewfriendsbuddy @ gmail . com) and if you have blood on our hands(radio mix)or 320 mp3s of live iTunes sessions(my were encoded from lower bit-rate) please mail me too.
I made new rips for yaw,iam as the last was not good!
